title: CES 2017 - Alpine R-Series Overview
description:
Abt Electronics talks to Alpine about their R-Series products.

R-Series Speakers:

R-S65C 6.5 Inch Component 2-Way Speakers

CTA-2031 Specifications: 100W RMS, 300W Peak, 4 Ohm
Frequency Response: 65Hz-29kHz
Available March; SRI: $330
R-S65 R-Series 6 1/2-inch Coaxial 2-Way Speakers

CTA-2031 Specifications: 100W RMS, 300W Peak, 4 Ohm
Frequency Response 65Hz-29kHz
1-inch Silk Tweeter
Available March; SRI: $230
R-S69 R-Series 6x9-inch Coaxial 2-Way Speakers

CTA-2031 Specifications: 100W RMS, 300W Peak, 4 Ohm
Frequency Response 60Hz-29kHz
1-inch Silk Tweeter
Available March; SRI: $230
R-S68 R-Series 6x8-inch Coaxial 2-Way Speakers

CTA-2031 Specifications: 100W RMS, 300W Peak, 4 Ohm
Frequency Response 63Hz-29kHz
1-inch Silk Tweeter
Available March; SRI: $230

Learn More: http://www.alpine-usa.com/company/press/ces2017/2017/alpine-electronics-redesigns-its-sound-system-philosophy-with-alpine-id
